&lt;p&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;NEW: DevDocs now comes with syntax highlighting. &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL2RldmRvY3MuaW8=&#34;&gt;http://devdocs.io&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
